- Table (with create CTA): `portal/admin/features/vehicles/table/vehicle-table-page.component.*`
- Form (create/edit): `portal/admin/features/users/form/user-form-page.component.*`
- Dashboard: `portal/admin/features/dashboard/admin-dashboard-page.component.*`
- Placeholder: `portal/pages/page-placeholder/page-placeholder.component.*`

